sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client<br/>(Dashboard/API)
    participant EvalHub as eval-hub API<br/>8080/TCP HTTPS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant JobPod as Job Pod
    participant Init as eval-runtime-init
    participant Adapter as Evaluation Adapter
    participant Sidecar as eval-runtime-sidecar<br/>8080/TCP localhost
    participant S3 as S3 Object Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MLflow as MLflow Tracking Server<br/>HTTPS
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,OCI: Flow 1: Evaluation Job Execution (Kubernetes)

    Client->>EvalHub: POST /api/v1/evaluations/jobs<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (K8s SA)
    EvalHub->>K8sAPI: TokenReview<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>EvalHub: TokenReview Response (authenticated user)
    EvalHub->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>trustyai.opendatahub.io/evaluations:create
    K8sAPI-->>EvalHub: SAR Response (allowed)

    EvalHub->>K8sAPI: Create ConfigMap<br/>(job.json + sidecar_config.json)
    K8sAPI-->>EvalHub: ConfigMap Created
    EvalHub->>K8sAPI: Create Batch Job<br/>(init + sidecar + adapter containers)
    K8sAPI-->>EvalHub: Job Created
    EvalHub-->>Client: 201 Created (job_id)

    Note over JobPod,S3: Job Pod Starts (KEP-753 Native Sidecars)

    activate Init
    Init->>S3: Download test data<br/>Auth: AWS IAM credentials
    S3-->>Init: Test data files
    deactivate Init

    activate Sidecar
    Note over Sidecar: Sidecar starts (RestartPolicy=Always)<br/>Startup probe: 30x2s

    activate Adapter
    Adapter->>Sidecar: POST /api/v1/evaluations/jobs/{id}/events<br/>localhost:8080 HTTP (plaintext, pod-local)
    Sidecar->>EvalHub: Forward status event<br/>HTTPS 8080, SA Token injected
    EvalHub-->>Sidecar: 200 OK
    Sidecar-->>Adapter: 200 OK

    Adapter->>Sidecar: POST /api/2.0/mlflow/runs/create<br/>localhost:8080
    Sidecar->>MLflow: Create MLflow run<br/>HTTPS, Projected SA Token
    MLflow-->>Sidecar: Run ID
    Sidecar-->>Adapter: Run ID

    Adapter->>Sidecar: POST /api/2.0/mlflow/runs/log-metric<br/>localhost:8080
    Sidecar->>MLflow: Log metrics<br/>HTTPS, Projected SA Token
    MLflow-->>Sidecar: OK
    Sidecar-->>Adapter: OK

    Adapter->>Sidecar: PUT /v2/{repo}/blobs/uploads/<br/>localhost:8080
    Sidecar->>OCI: Push evaluation artifacts<br/>HTTPS 443, Bearer Token (challenge-response)
    OCI-->>Sidecar: Upload complete
    Sidecar-->>Adapter: Upload complete

    Adapter->>Sidecar: POST /api/v1/evaluations/jobs/{id}/events<br/>status: completed
    Sidecar->>EvalHub: Job completed event<br/>HTTPS 8080
    EvalHub-->>Sidecar: OK
    Sidecar-->>Adapter: OK
    deactivate Adapter
    deactivate Sidecar

    Note over Client,OCI: Flow 2: Authentication & Authorization

    Client->>EvalHub: GET /api/v1/evaluations/jobs<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    EvalHub->>K8sAPI: TokenReview (cached 2 min)
    K8sAPI-->>EvalHub: User identity
    EvalHub->>K8sAPI: SAR (cached 5 min allow / 30s deny)<br/>namespace from X-Tenant header
    K8sAPI-->>EvalHub: Authorized
    EvalHub->>EvalHub: Query Storage<br/>(PostgreSQL 5432/TCP or SQLite)
    EvalHub-->>Client: 200 OK (jobs list)
